# Tango Icons Plugin #

The sfTangoIconsPlugin offers a set of [Tango](http://tango.freedesktop.org/Tango_Icon_Library) icons in sizes 16x16, 22x22 and 32x32.

## Installation ##

  * Install the plugin

        $ symfony plugin:install sfTangoIconsPlugin

  * Clear cache

        $ symfony cc

## Configuration ##

  * You can set the default size of icons in app.yml:

        all:
          tango_icons:
            size: <?php echo TangoIconsSize::SMALL ?>

  * Activate helper in settings.yml:

        standard_helpers: [...TangoIcons]

    or:

        use_helper('TangoIcons');

## Use ##

If you have selected the default size of icons:

    <img src="<?php echo ti_get_image_path('actions', 'go-home') ?>" alt="" />

If you do not have determined the size of the default icons, or want to manually set the size of icons:

    <img src="<?php echo ti_get_image_path('actions', 'go-home', TangoIconsSize::SMALL) ?>" alt="" />

